{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create an ultra-premium professional Shopify reels/video showcase section compatible with Shopify Liquid.
    
    IMPORTANT:
    - This is for SHOPIFY
    - Must work as a Shopify custom section
    - Use Shopify Liquid schema
    - Merchant should be able to upload/manage videos directly from Shopify Theme Customizer
    - NO headings
    - NO titles
    - NO captions
    - NO extra text
    - ONLY the reel/video section itself
    
    SHOPIFY REQUIREMENTS:
    - Create a fully functional Shopify section
    - Use:
      - Liquid
      - HTML
      - CSS
      - JavaScript
    - Include complete Shopify schema
    - Add support for at least 15 video blocks
    - Merchant uploads videos from Theme Editor
    - Empty blocks should remain hidden automatically
    - Entire section hidden if no videos uploaded
    - Fully customizable through Shopify editor
    
    LAYOUT:
    - Horizontal draggable reels carousel
    - Show:
      - 4 videos on desktop
      - 2 videos on tablet
      - 1 video on mobile
    - Remaining videos hidden outside viewport
    - Smooth draggable/swipe interaction
    - Mouse drag support
    - Touch swipe support
    - Snap scrolling
    - Momentum/inertia movement
    - Premium cinematic spacing
    
    VIDEO CARDS:
    - Vertical 9:16 reel cards
    - Auto-play immediately
    - Muted
    - Loop infinitely
    - NO controls visible in carousel
    - Videos should use object-fit: cover
    - No black bars
    - Lazy loading enabled
    - Smooth hover interactions
    
    CARD EFFECTS:
    - Hover scale animation
    - Soft premium shadow glow
    - Slight lift effect
    - Smooth border highlight
    - Premium glassmorphism feel
    - Cursor changes to grabbing while dragging
    - Subtle cinematic gradient overlay
    
    FULLSCREEN EXPERIENCE:
    When user clicks any reel:
    - Open fullscreen modal overlay
    - Dark blurred cinematic background
    - Large centered responsive video player
    - Prevent background scrolling while modal open
    
    FULLSCREEN CONTROLS:
    - Play/Pause
    - Timeline/progress bar
    - Draggable scrubber like VLC/media player
    - Click timeline to jump timestamp
    - Current time and total duration
    - Volume control
